      <title>RYZEN 9 9950X3D &amp; RADEON 9070XT ＆ DDR5 6000CL30</title>
      <link>https://yuki9902-jp.github.io/posts/2025-12-11_ryzen-9-9950x3d--radeon-9070xt--ddr5-6000cl30/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Dec 2025 12:55:46 +0900</pubDate>
